# Terraform working directories
**/.terraform/

# Terraform state and local plans
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*
**/planfile*

**/secrets**

# Local Python environments and notebook artifacts
**/.venv/
**/.venv-*/
**/.ipynb_checkpoints/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.coverage
**/.tox/
**/htmlcov/

# React/Node build artifacts
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.vite/
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pnpm-debug.log*

# Docker local artifacts
**/.docker/
**/docker-compose.override.yml

# Kubernetes local files
**/.kube/
**/kubeconfig
**/kubeconfig.*

# Environment files (keep templates tracked)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.*.example

# Local diagnostics bundles
gke-diagnostics-*.tgz

# Local DBs
**/*.db

